					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5360756#post-3723212</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5360756/scp-3395#post-3723212</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2018 01:13:42 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ObserverSeptember</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1488791</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>15 Jan 2000: Khalid al-Mihdhar and Nawaf Al-Hazmi (Flight 77/Pentagon Hijackers) arrive in the United States.</p> <p>18 May 2000: Mohammed Atta (Flight 11/North Tower Hijacker-Pilot) applies for and receives a US visa.</p> <p>11 Sep 2000: One year before 9/11, section was referencing <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Cosgrove">this guy</a> (WARNING: Call is NSFL)</p> <p>31 Dec 2000: No significance, last day of the year.</p> <p>23 Aug 2001: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_P._O%27Neill">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_P._O%27Neill</a></p> <p>The offices in which the entity manifests were all areas that were in or above the impact zone of the airplanes on 9/11. Marsh &amp; McLennan spanned the impact zone of the North Tower, Cantor Fitzgerald was above the North Tower impact zone (and lost more employees than any other company or the City of New York), and Aon Corporation was located above the South Tower impact zone.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
